So, as before, we going to grab a generator object, this time called `bumps`.

We will do the same thing again and generate something from the README, and I’ll open that in [an image editing app](https://flyingmeat.com/acorn/) with [another convenience method](https://github.com/h-lame/stegosaurus/blob/24ec34dff57062ac9edd075163d1c9b8c2c26d08/lib/stegosaurus.rb#L24-L26).

